    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i think i'm done with the expectations and the weight. it's just so much easier to stop fighting the wind. when you're standing right at the edge of that cliff, looking at the dark, it doesn't even feel scary anymore. it just feels like a place where everything finally goes quiet. maybe the silence is the only thing that actually makes sense now.",
